dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.transportprotocols

Interface IFlexRayTpChannel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, ITpChannel

    public interface IFlexRayTpChannel
extends IEntity, ITpChannel
    IFlexRayTpChannel: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A channel is a group of connections sharing several properties. The FlexRay Transport Layer supports several channels. These channels can work concurrently, thus each of them requires its own state machine and management data structures and its own PDU-IDs.

      • getFlowControlPdu

        INPdu getFlowControlPdu()
        Query the undirectional to-one association FlowControlPdu.

        Reference to the Flow Control NPdu. The Flow Control network protocol data unit (FC N_PDU) is identified by the Flow Control protocol control information (FC N_PCI). The Flow Control network protocol data unit (FC N_PDU) instructs a sending network entity to start, stop or resume transmission of CF N_PDUs. The Flow Control network protocol data unit shall be sent by the receiving network layer entity to the sending network layer entity, when ready to receive more data, after correct reception of:
